<h3>Example Recipe ( 100% inedible )</h3>
<ul>
	<li>1 Cup of flour</li>
	<li> 1 Cup of butter</li>
	<li>1/2 Sugar</li>
	<li> 2 Eggs</li>
	<li> 1 Tbsp. Lemon zest</li>
	<li> 2 Cups of blueberries</li>
	<li> 1 Dash of vanilla</li>
</ul>
<h3>Subtitle for instructions</h3>
<p class="caption"> this is where you could list steps for instructions </p>
<ol>
	<li> Preheat oven to 400 degrees</li>
	<li> cream butter and sugar together, once creamed together add vanilla</li>
	<li> whisk in two eggs </li>
	<li> Mix in flour </li>
	<li>Fold in blueberries and lemon zest</li>
	<li>Bake for 25 minutes in preheated oven</li>
</ol>
